\id 1JN - Borna New Testamnet
\h 1 Yohans
\toc2 1 Yohans
\toc1 1 Yohans Woshts Wosho
\toc3 1 Yoh.
\mt1 Wosheetso Yohans Shints Wosho
\imt1 Kindo
\ip Woshetso Yohans shino b́ woshts wosho keewi een een git asaabiyotsi biitse detsfe. Bowere han nababituwots Ik'onat Naayo Iyesus Krstosnton ik woto bo detsetwok'o boon kup'iyonat ik wotmanowere t'afiy falitu kootetsuwots bo danirudnatse boatso bokotetuwok'oshe. Manoori tuuts kootets kooti dani gondo t'uup't keshiruwatse be'eyiru datsanton k'aleyiru gonkeyo b́wottsotse, Ik'o naay Iyesus b́jamon ashwoto wee ash nai amalo detso falratse etiiruwoni b́teshi. Daniru manots «Wora eto datsatsi beyosh kic'otse nas' kesha eta» boetfooni b́teshi. Mantonuwere «Sheeng amal detso wotowa ash k'oshosh shun kitso woronton eegor gonkewo» deshatse eta boetfo boteshi.
\ip Han Guut'tso danan k'efat Iyesus Krstos ari ashe, Iyesusi amaniruwotsnat Ik' shuniru jamwotsn boatsatseyosh shunewo boosh geyife ett keewure.
\iot Jamon mas'aafan b́detstso
\io1 Kindo 1:1-4
\io1 Shaanonat t'aluwona 1:5—2:29
\io1 Ik'i nanaúwotsnat Diyablos nana'otsn 3:1-24
\io1 Aroonat sheelon 4:1-6
\io1 Shuno b́k'alit k'alo 4:7-21
\io1 Da'ts imnetiyo 5:1-21
\c 1
\s1 Kash aap'o
\p 
\v 1 Shin teshts kashi aap'i jango itsh guut'irwonee, kashi aap'anuwere no shishtsonat no aawon nobek'tso, nos'iiltsonat nokishonowere noshu'utsoniye.
\v 2 Kashanwere be'ere noowere bín bek'rone, no b́ jangosh gawitwone. Nihoke teshtsonat noosh be'ets dúre dúri kasho itsh keewitwone.
\v 3 Noonton ik woto itdetseetwek'o nobek'tsok'onat noshishtson itsh keewirwone. Ik nowotitwere nihonat b́ naay Iyesus Krstosntoniye.
\v 4 Nogeneeúwo s'een b́wototiwok'o han itsh guut'irwone.
\s1 Ik'o sháán b́wottsok'o
\p 
\v 5 Bíyokee noshishtsonat itsh nokewit wosho «Ik'o shááne, t'aluwonwere b́jamon bíyoke aaliye» etiruwoniye.
\v 6 Mansh «Ik'onton ik woto detsfone» erfetsr t'aluwotse nobeetka wotiyal koote nokotiri, no aap'onat nofino arikaliye etee.
\v 7 Wotowa eree bí sháánotse b́ beyirwok'o noowere sháánotse nobeyink'e no atsatsewo ik wotosh faliyank'one. Dab b́ naay Iyesus Krstos s'atsonwor morr jamotse noon s'aytsitwee.
\p 
\v 8 Morro deshatsone no'etal notooke no ant'elciri, aronwere noytse aaliye.
\v 9 No morro Ik'osh kish nokewitka wotiyal bí kááwonat amanek b́wottsosh nomorr jamo noosh orowa eteetwe nogond fin jamatsno noon s'ayintsitwe.
\v 10 Morro fineratsone no'etetkawotiyal Ik'one kotetsiye nowoshiri, bí aap'onwere noyitse aali etee.
\c 2
\s1 Iyesus Krstos noosh ned'tso b́wottsok'o
\p 
\v 1 T nana'otso! han itsh tguut'ir morro itfinerawok'owa etaatniye. Wotowa eree konunoru b́ wotiyal asho morro b́finiyal nihokere noosh ned'itwo detsfone, bíwere kááwo Iyesus Krstosiye.
\v 2 Bí nomorro t'afibazetwe, nomorr mec'rosh b́woterawon dats jami morro t'afibazetwo bíne.
\p 
\v 3 Ik'i tzaziya no s'eentsiri wotiyal bín dank nowottsok'o manne nokitsiti.
\v 4 «Ik'o danfee» et fetst b́ tzaziyotsi s'eentsrawo fa'e wotiyal kootetskee, arikeewonwere b́gitsotse aaliye.
\v 5 Ernmó Ik'i aap'osh aleyiru jamo Ik'osh b́ detsts shuno arikee, arikon bín beyirwotsi nowottsok'owo b́ danet manne,
\v 6 Ik'ontoniye tbeyiri etiru asho Krstos beyiruwok'o beyo bísh geyife.
\s1 Handr tzaziyo
\p 
\v 7 T shuntswotso! itsh t guut'iru tzaziyan shin shinon it detsts yotstsuniye bako handriyaliye, yoots tzaziyanwere it shihsts aap'oniye.
\v 8 Wotowa eree Krstosnat itoke ar wotat be'etso handr tzaziyoniye itsh tguut'iri, t'aluwo k'aaú b́bazere ari shááno and sháánirwe.
\p 
\v 9 Sháánatse beyiruwe etfetst bí'eshuwi shit'irwo andoor t'aluwotse b́ fa'oni.
\v 10 Bí eshwi shuniru jamo sháánatse b́beyiri, bíyoknowere ashosh t'ug wotit keewo daatseratse.
\v 11 Bí eshuwi shit'irwonmó t'aluwotsene b́beyiri, t'aluwotsnowere bíananiri, t'aluwonwere bíaawo dek b́k'rtsotse bíamirwoko dande'atse.
\p 
\v 12 T nana'úwotso! it morro Iyesus shúútson itsh orowe etetsotsne itsh t guut'iri.
\v 13 Nih nihuwotso! shintson beyirwo itdantsotsene itsh guut'irwe. Jawetswotsnat baaruwotso! shed'ano it da'atsotsne itsh t guut'iri.
\v 14 Nana'úwotso! Niho itdantsotsene itsh t guut'iriye, nihuwotso, shin shino teshtso it dantsotsne itsh tguut'iye. Jawetsonat baaruwotso! kup'uwotsi it wottswotsnat Ik'i aap'o it nibotse b́beyrwotse, shed'anonowere itda'atsotse itsh guut're.
\p 
\v 15 Datsani wotowa datsank wotts keew jamo shunk'ayere. Datsani shunetwo Ik'o niho shuno bíatsotse aaliye.
\v 16 Datsuatse beyru jamo meets tewuno, ááw mirac'o, b́ beewon it'o datsatsika bako Ik'o nihokikaliye.
\v 17 Datsannat b́ tewunonowere beshitke. Ernmó Ik' shuntsok'o k'alituwo dúre dúroshe b́ beeti.
\s1 Krstosi k'efirwotsatse ni atso korde'e
\p 
\v 18 T nana'otso! hań s'uwaatsi sa'atoniye, «Krstosi k'efitwo weetwe» eteere shishrte, hamb, dab́ andoor Krstosi k'efiru aywots tuurnee, manatse tuutson s'uwaatsi sa'at b́woto manne nodaniye.
\v 19 Bo noyitsne bokeshi. Wotowa eree yotsor nojirnaliye, nojirno wotink'ere noonton kup'arniye bobeyank'oni. Ernmó boúnetswor nojir wotbok'azo b́danetwok'o noyitse galeyat k'azkeshrnee.
\p 
\v 20 Itnmó S'ayin shayiron Krstos fuutk'rere. Mansh it jamets ún keewo danfte.
\v 21 Itsh t guut'ir ariko itdartsoshaliye, itiyere aro danfte, arotsnowere kooto b́datserawok'o danfte.
\p 
\v 22 Eshe Iyesus Krstosi b́ wottsok'osh haalirwoniyere okoon kone kotetsoni? Bí Krstosi k'efirwoniye, Nihonat naayo noowere haalitwe.
\v 23 Naayo halitwonu nihonowere de'atse, na'on amantso nihono amanere.
\p 
\v 24 Shin shintson it shishts keewman it nibotse s'ap'de'er beewe, itmó shin shintson it shishtsman it nibotse s'ap'de'er b́ betka wotiyal na'onat nihonton ik woto detsetute.
\v 25 Manwere Krstos shinomaants noosh jangit b́imetso dúre dúr kashoniye.
\p 
\v 26 Itn dariyiru ashuwotsatse tuutsone han t guut'i,
\v 27 Krstosoke itdek'ts shayiri S'ayno ititse b́ beyrwosh k'oshodanitwo itsh geyiratse, bíwere jam keewo itsh danituwe, itsh b́ danitwonu ara bako kootaliye mansh shayiri S'ayno itn b́ danitsok'on Krstoston wotde'er beewere,.
\p 
\v 28 Eshe t nana'otso! bí b́be'ewor nosharaniyere aawo shu'úde'er bín nobek'etwok'onat bí b́weet aawots b́ shinatse nojitserawok'o bíń beewere,,
\v 29 Bíwere kááwo b́wotok'o it daniyakon, kááw finiru jamo Ik'oke shuwek b́ wottsok'o dande'ere.
\c 3
\s1 Ik' nana'úwotsi
\p 
\v 1 Ik' nana'uwotsi erŕ nos'eegeetwok'o niho awuk'o shuno noosh b́imtsok'o aab́ s'iilere! arikon noowere Ik' nana'a noone, datsan Ik'o b́dartsosh nonowere danatse.
\v 2 T shuntswotso! and no Ik' nana'a noone, shinomaantsish eeg nowotitwok'o daneerafa'ee, ernmó Krstos b́be'et aawots bí aro arikon eeg bíarok'o nobek'etwotse bínowere noaritwok'ó danfone.
\v 3 Krstosn man b́ wotitwok'o jangiru jamo Krstos s'ayn b́ wottsok'o bíwere b́ tooko s'ayn woshituwe.
\p 
\v 4 Morra eto Ik' nemo gaak b́ wottsotse morr finit jamo Ik' nemo gáákre.
\v 5 Ashuwots morro t'afiyosh Krstos b́be'etsok'onat bíwere morro b́ deshawok'o danfte.
\v 6 Eshe Krstosnton beet ash jamo morro fineratse. Morr finitu asho Krstosi be'atse, bínowere danatse.
\p 
\v 7 T nana'uwotso! konworu itn bí ant'elcerawok'owa, Krstos kááwo b́ wottsok'o kááwts fino k'alitu jamo kááwe.
\v 8 Diyablos shintson dek'tut morro b́ finirwosh morr finiru ash jamo Diyablos jiire. Ik' na'o b́ be'e diyablos fino gakoshee.
\p 
\v 9 Ik'i doyo b́gitsotse b́beyirwotsnat Ik'atse b́shuwetsotse Ik'i na'a wottso morro fineratse, finoshowere falratse.
\v 10 Ik' nana'onat Diyablos nana'on galde danet hanne, Kááw finerawonat bí eshuwi shunaw jamonúwots Ik' nana'analiye.
\s1 Atsatsewo shuneyi jango
\p 
\v 11 Shin shintson it k'ebts wosho «No atsatsewo shunewone» etirwoniye.
\v 12 Shed'ani jir teshtsonat bíeshuwi úd'tso K'ayelkok'o woto geyiratse, bí bíeshuwi eegishe b́ úd'i? B́ fino gond b́ teshtsotsnat bí eshu fino kááw b́ teshtsotsne.
\p 
\v 13 Ti eshuwotso! datsatsi ashuwots iti boshit'al mansh adk'ayere.
\v 14 Noo no eshuwotsi noshunirwotse k'iromaantse kashomaants k'az nokimtsok'o danfone. Shun deshaw asho k'iri c'ishotse b́beyri.
\v 15 Bíeshuwi shit'iru jamo kash úd'kee, kash úd'tsonmó dúredúri kasho b́daatsrawok'o danfte.
\v 16 Shuno eeg b́wottsok'o nodanet Iyesus Krstos b́ kasho noosh b́imtsoshe, noowere nokasho no eshuwotssh beshide imo noosh geyife.
\v 17 Datsanatse gaalo deshfetsr kic'iru asho be'efetsr maac' k'eweraw asho «Ik'o shunfee» eto awuk'o k'alrniya b́faliti?
\v 18 T nana'otso! No shuno arikonat finon be'etka bako noonon mec'ron keewon wotk'aye.
\s1 Ik'i shinatse nodetsts ááwu shuuk'o
\p 
\v 19 Mannowere arkeewtswotsi nowottsok'onat Ik'ishinats t'inosh shatalon aaw shuk'on t'inosh nofalitwok'o danfone.
\v 20 Nonibo noats bíangshiyalor Ik'o noniboniyere danbe, bíye jamkeewo danfee.
\v 21 T shuntswotso! No nibo noats angshratse wotiyal Ik'i shinatse ááw shuuk'o detsetwonee.
\v 22 Ik'i tzazi jamo s'eentsr bín gene'úshit keewo nofinitwotse nok'onitu jamo bíyoke daatsitwone.
\v 23 Ik'o azaztsonu b́ naay Iyesus Krstos shútson amanar Krstos noon bíazaztsok'on noatsatsewo noshunetwok'owe.
\v 24 Ik'o azaztso k'alitu jamwots Ik'ona bobeti, Ik'onwere boyitse b́beeti, Ik'o noyitse b́beyirwok'o nodanet noosh b́ imts S'ayin shayirone.
\c 4
\s1 Ari shayironat kooti shayiron
\p 
\v 1 T shuntswotso! datsatse kotetsk wotts nebiyiwots botutsotse shayr jamwotsi aman k'ayere, maniyere shayirwots Ik'okik bowotonat wotbok'azo fads'iilere.
\v 2 Ik' Shayiro b́ woto galde'e it danet hanne Iyesus Krstos meetson b́ be'etsok'o amants shayir jamo Ik'i shayire,
\v 3 Iyesus Krstos ash wotat meetso tahadek't b́be'etsok'o amaneraw shayir jamo Ik'oki shayiraliye, shayiraanu weetwe etefere itshishtso Krstosi k'efiru shayironiye, bíwere andoru dab́ datsuatse fa'ee.
\p 
\v 4 Nana'otso! It Ik'k itne, ititse beyru shayiro datsanatse fa'a shayironiyere bogfe. Eshe kotets nebiyotsi da'artee.
\v 5 Kootets nebiyots datsatsikne, bokeewirwonu datsanatsi keewoniye. Datsanwere bokeewo k'ebetwane.
\v 6 No Ik'ik noone, Ik' dants jamo no keewo k'ebetwe, Ik'ik woteraw jamonmó no keewo k'ewatse. Ari shayronat kooti shayiron nodanet hanne.
\s1 Ik'o shune
\p 
\v 7 Shunetswotsó! shuno Ik'okik b́wottsotse no atsatsewo shunewone, shuniru jamo Ik'i na'ee, Ik'onowere danfee.
\v 8 Ik'o shun b́wottsotse ash shunaw jamo Ik'o danatse.
\v 9 Ik'o b́naayn kasho nodaatsitwok'o b́ naay ik s'uzo datsanats woshere, mannowere Ik'i shuno nodagotse be'ere.
\v 10 Shuna eto hank'oyiye, no Ik'o noshuntsosh b́ woterawo bí noon b́ shuntsonat nomorro b́ t'afitwok'o b́ naayi b́woshtsoshee.
\p 
\v 11 Shunetswotsó! Ik'o hank'o noon b́shuniyakon no noatsatsewo shunewo noon geyife.
\v 12 Ik' bek'ts asho konwor aaliye. Noo noatsatsewo noshuneyink'ere Ik'o noyitse beyank'ee, b́ shunonwere noyitse s'een wotiyank'ee.
\p 
\v 13 Ik'o b́ shayiro nooshowere b́'imtsotse no bín bíwere noyitse b́ beyirwok'owo danfone.
\v 14 Niho datsani b́ kashitwok'o woshdek't naayo b́wooshtsok'o bek'rone, manowere gawitwone.
\v 15 Iyesus Ik'o naayi b́ wottsok'o amanitu ashotsne Ik'o b́beeti, bíwere Ik'ootse b́beeti.
\v 16 Mann Ik'o noosh b́detsts shuno danfone, manowere amanerone. Ik'o shune, shunon beyirwo Ik'one b́beyiri, Ik'onwere b́ gitsotse b́beyiri.
\v 17 Noo datsanatse nobeyir ari Krstos b́beyirwok'o b́wottsotse noshuno s'een b́wotink'ere angshi aawots shatalon b́shinaatse aaw shuk'on t'inosh falyank'onee.
\v 18 S'een shuno shato kishde'erni juubk'rti bako shunotse shato aaliye, shato sezonton deshk b́wottsotse shatiru asho b́shuno s'een woteratse.
\p 
\v 19 Ik'o shin shintson nonb́shuntsotse noowere shunetwonee.
\v 20 Ik'o shunfee etfetst bíeshuwi shit'irwo kotetsiye, b́ bek'tso bí'eshuwi shunatse wotiyal b́ be'aaw Ik'o shuno falratse.
\v 21 Eshe Krstos noosh b́'imts tzaziyo Ik' shuntso bíeshuno shune erkee.
\c 5
\s1 Datsu imnetiyon da'o
\p 
\v 1 Iyesus Mesihiyo b́ wottsok'o amants jamwots Ik' nana'anee, nihono shunetu jamo naayo noowere shunfee.
\v 2 Ik' nana'úwotsi noshuntsok'o nodanetiye, Ik'o shunr b́ tzaziyo no s'entsoree.
\v 3 Ik' shuna eto b́ tzaziyotsi s'entsee. B́ tzaziyotsu mangnaliye.
\v 4 Ik' nana'a wotts jamo datsu da'itwe, datsu no da'itwere imnetiyone.
\v 5 Iyesus Ik'o naayi b́ wottsok'o amantsoni bako kone datsu da'itwoni?
\s1 Krstos jangosh gawets gawo
\p 
\v 6 Aatsots b́ gupetsok'o kitsit aatsonat b́ k'iro kitsru s'atsi weeron waatso Iyesus Krstosiye. Bí b́waa aats mec'ron b́ woterawo aatsonat s'atsone. Hanwere ar b́ wottsotse, keewanwere ar b́wottsok'owo S'ayin shayiron gawitwe.
\v 7 Keez gawwots fa'ane,
\v 8 Bowere Shayirona, aatsonat s'atsone, keezanotswere bogawon ikne.
\v 9 Ashuwots bo gawts gawo dek'etwonee, ernmó Ik'o gawts gawonmó jamoniyere bogfe. Ik'o b́ gawtsonwere b́ naay jangosh b́ gawtsoniyee haniye.
\v 10 Ik'o naayn amantsonmó gawan b́ gitsotse fa'ee, Ik' amanerawonmó Ik'o b́ naay jangosh b́'imts gawo aman b́ k'aztsatse tuutson Ik'o kootetsi woshre.
\v 11 B́ gawonwere Ik'o dúre dúri kasho noosh b́ imtsok'onat kashmanwere b́ naayitse b́ beyirwok'o gawirwoniyee.
\v 12 Ik'o naayi detstso kasho detsfe. Ik'o naayi deshawonmó kasho deshatse.
\s1 Dúre dúri kasha
\p 
\v 13 It Ik'o naay shútson amants jamwots dúre dúri kasho it detstsok'o it danishe han itsh guut're.
\v 14 Kon naari keewonor b́ wotiyal b́ shuntsok'on nok'onitkawotiyal noosh b́ shishetwok'o amanitwone.
\v 15 Noo k'onts jamo b́ shishetwok'o danfonewotiyal, bíyokere nok'onts jamo andon nodek'etwok'o danfone.
\p 
\v 16 Konworu wotowa, ash iko bí eshu k'irosh bín betsaw morro b́ finefe b́bek'al bísh Ik'o k'onwe, ashman morro k'irosh bín betsatse wotiyal Ik'o kasho bísh imetwe. Ernmó k'irosh betsit morro fa'ee. Man naari morrosh Ik'o k'onuwe eraatse taa.
\v 17 Gond fin jamo morre. Wotowa eree k'irosh betsraw morro fa'ee.
\p 
\v 18 Ik' na'o Iyesus Krstos bín b́ kotirwosh Ik' na'a wotts jamo morro b́ finerawok'o danfone, Shed'anonwere bíats boratse.
\p 
\v 19 Noo Ik'k nowottsok'o danfone. Datsunmó jamon shed'ani ali shirotse b́ fa'oni.
\p 
\v 20 Ik' na'o b́ wattsok'onat ari Ik'o nodanetwok'o t'iwitsts nibo noosh b́'imtsok'o danfone, b́ naay Iyesus Krstos weeron bínton ari Ik'onton ikwoto detsfone. Iyesus Krstos ari Izar Izeweru dúre dúri kashonu bíne.
\p 
\v 21 T nana'otso! dozets ik'wotsatse it atso korde'ere.
